<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>調味製程通風安全與人員暴露評估資訊圖表</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chartjs-plugin-annotation@1.4.0"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
        }
        .chart-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            height: 40vh;
            max-height: 400px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .chart-container {
                height: 50vh;
                max-height: 350px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">

    <div class="container mx-auto p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8">
        <header class="text-center mb-8">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#005f73]">調味製程通風安全與人員暴露評估</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-red-600 mt-2"> ethanol-based flavoring process risk analysis</p>
        </header>

        <main class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

            <section class="lg:col-span-3 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a9396] mb-4">情境概述：潛在的雙重風險</h2>
                <p class="text-base mb-4">一家食品製造商在開發新產品時，計畫使用一個加熱通風滾筒為零食進行乙醇基底的調味塗層。此製程雖然能有效生產，卻引發了兩個關鍵的環安衛(EHS)疑慮：排氣管道內的 **爆炸風險** 與作業區內的 **勞工健康暴露風險**。本評估旨在量化這些風險並提出控制建議。</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-8 text-center mt-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-4xl">🥣</span>
                        <p class="font-semibold">乙醇漿料</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-2xl text-[#94d2bd] font-bold">→</div>
                    <div class="p-4 border-2 border-dashed border-[#94d2bd] rounded-lg">
                        <p class="text-4xl">🔥</p>
                        <p class="font-semibold mt-2">加熱通風滾筒</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-2xl text-[#94d2bd] font-bold">→</div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
                         <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                            <span class="text-4xl">🍿</span>
                            <p class="font-semibold">成品</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-red-600">
                            <span class="text-4xl">💨</span>
                            <p class="font-semibold">含乙醇廢氣</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#ca6702] mb-2">爆炸下限 (LEL)</h3>
                <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#bb3e03]">3.3%</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">(33,000 ppm)</p>
                <p class="mt-4">空氣中乙醇濃度若超過此值，遇到火源即可能引發爆炸，是首要的安全紅線。</p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0a9396] mb-2">職業暴露容許濃度 (PEL)</h3>
                <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#005f73]">1,000 ppm</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">(8小時日時量平均)</p>
                <p class="mt-4">勞工每日工作8小時的平均暴露量不應超過此法定標準，以保護長期健康。</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#ca6702] mb-2">評估關鍵物質</h3>
                <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#005f73]">乙醇</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">(Ethanol)</p>
                <p class="mt-4">作為漿料的主要溶劑，其高揮發性與可燃性是本次風險評估的核心。</p>
            </section>


            <section class="lg:col-span-3 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#ae2012] mb-2">安全風險評估：排氣管內的定時炸彈</h2>
                <p class="text-base mb-4">模型分析顯示，雖然20分鐘的平均濃度(1.8%)看似安全，但更真實的「指數遞減模型」揭示了致命的真相：在製程 **開始後的3-4分鐘內**，排氣管內的乙醇濃度將會 **飆升並超過3.3%的爆炸下限**，構成極高的安全風險。</p>
                <div class="chart-container">
                    <canvas id="exhaustChart"></canvas>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="lg:col-span-2 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a9396] mb-2">職業衛生暴露評估：逸散至作業區的風險</h2>
                <p class="text-base mb-4">經評估，滾筒入口的捕集效率僅達建議標準的下限。保守估計約有10%的乙醇蒸氣逸散至作業區。模型計算顯示，勞工短時間暴露濃度約為 **450 ppm**，雖然低於法規標準，但仍是不可忽視的潛在暴露，應依循合理抑低(ALARA)原則進行改善。</p>
                <div class="chart-container h-64 sm:h-80 md:h-96 max-h-[300px]">
                    <canvas id="exposureChart"></canvas>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="lg:col-span-1 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#005f73] mb-4">總結與建議</h2>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-2xl mr-3">🚨</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#ae2012]">立即停止作業</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm">製程存在明確且嚴重的爆炸隱患，必須立即停止直到改善方案到位。</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-2xl mr-3">🛠️</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#ca6702]">強化工程控制</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm">優先考慮增加排氣系統的抽氣量，以同時降低管道濃度並提升入口捕集效率。</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-2xl mr-3">📋</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#ee9b00]">調整管理方法</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm">若工程改善受限，應評估調整漿料配方（如降低乙醇含量）的可行性。</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-2xl mr-3">🔬</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0a9396]">執行驗證監測</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm">任何改善措施實施後，必須重新評估並進行現場採樣，確保風險已被有效控制。</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

        </main>
        
        <footer class="text-center mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-gray-300">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">參考資料：Chapter 9 Ventilation Requirements for a Flavoring Process</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">made by Peter Ho. 114.08.16</p>
        </footer>

    </div>

    <script>
        const brilliantBlues = {
            darkBlue: '#005f73',
            teal: '#0a9396',
            lightTeal: '#94d2bd',
            sand: '#e9d8a6',
            yellowOrange: '#ee9b00',
            orange: '#ca6702',
            darkOrange: '#bb3e03',
            red: '#ae2012',
            darkRed: '#9b2226'
        };

        const tooltipConfig = {
            plugins: {
                tooltip: {
                    callbacks: {
                        title: function(tooltipItems) {
                            const item = tooltipItems[0];
                            let label = item.chart.data.labels[item.dataIndex];
                            if (Array.isArray(label)) {
                              return label.join(' ');
                            } else {
                              return label;
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        };

        function wrapLabel(str, maxWidth) {
            if (str.length <= maxWidth) return str;
            const words = str.split(' ');
            let lines = [];
            let currentLine = '';
            for (const word of words) {
                if ((currentLine + word).length > maxWidth && currentLine.length > 0) {
                    lines.push(currentLine.trim());
                    currentLine = '';
                }
                currentLine += word + ' ';
            }
            lines.push(currentLine.trim());
            return lines;
        }

        const exhaustCtx = document.getElementById('exhaustChart').getContext('2d');
        const exhaustChart = new Chart(exhaustCtx, {
            type: 'line',
            data: {
                labels: Array.from({ length: 21 }, (_, i) => i),
                datasets: [
                    {
                        label: '恆定蒸散率模型濃度 (%)',
                        data: Array(21).fill(1.8),
                        borderColor: brilliantBlues.teal,
                        backgroundColor: 'rgba(10, 147, 150, 0.1)',
                        borderWidth: 2,
                        pointRadius: 0,
                        tension: 0.1,
                        borderDash: [5, 5],
                    },
                    {
                        label: '指數遞減模型濃度 (%)',
                        data: [4.5, 4.1, 3.7, 3.4, 3.1, 2.8, 2.5, 2.3, 2.1, 1.9, 1.7, 1.5, 1.4, 1.2, 1.1, 1.0, 0.9, 0.8, 0.7, 0.6, 0.5],
                        borderColor: brilliantBlues.red,
                        backgroundColor: 'rgba(174, 32, 18, 0.2)',
                        borderWidth: 3,
                        pointRadius: 2,
                        tension: 0.4,
                        fill: true,
                    }
                ]
            },
            options: {
                ...tooltipConfig,
                maintainAspectRatio: false,
                responsive: true,
                scales: {
                    x: {
                        title: {
                            display: true,
                            text: '時間 (分鐘)'
                        }
                    },
                    y: {
                        title: {
                            display: true,
                            text: '乙醇濃度 (%)'
                        },
                        beginAtZero: true
                    }
                },
                plugins: {
                    ...tooltipConfig.plugins,
                    legend: {
                        position: 'top',
                    },
                    title: {
                        display: true,
                        text: '排氣管內乙醇濃度隨時間變化模擬',
                        font: {
                            size: 16
                        }
                    },
                    annotation: {
                        annotations: {
                            lelLine: {
                                type: 'line',
                                yMin: 3.3,
                                yMax: 3.3,
                                borderColor: brilliantBlues.darkRed,
                                borderWidth: 2,
                                borderDash: [6, 6],
                                label: {
                                    content: '爆炸下限 (LEL): 3.3%',
                                    enabled: true,
                                    position: 'end',
                                    backgroundColor: 'rgba(155, 34, 38, 0.8)',
                                    font: {
                                        weight: 'bold'
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        });

        const exposureCtx = document.getElementById('exposureChart').getContext('2d');
        const originalLabels = ['預估勞工暴露濃度', '法定容許暴露標準 (TWA-PEL)'];
        const wrappedLabels = originalLabels.map(label => wrapLabel(label, 16));

        const exposureChart = new Chart(exposureCtx, {
            type: 'bar',
            data: {
                labels: wrappedLabels,
                datasets: [{
                    label: '乙醇濃度 (ppm)',
                    data: [450, 1000],
                    backgroundColor: [
                        brilliantBlues.yellowOrange,
                        brilliantBlues.lightTeal,
                    ],
                    borderColor: [
                        brilliantBlues.orange,
                        brilliantBlues.teal,
                    ],
                    borderWidth: 1
                }]
            },
            options: {
                ...tooltipConfig,
                indexAxis: 'y',
                maintainAspectRatio: false,
                responsive: true,
                scales: {
                    x: {
                        beginAtZero: true,
                        title: {
                            display: true,
                            text: '濃度 (ppm)'
                        }
                    }
                },
                plugins: {
                    ...tooltipConfig.plugins,
                    legend: {
                        display: false
                    },
                    title: {
                        display: true,
                        text: '作業區暴露濃度 vs 法規標準',
                        font: {
                            size: 16
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>
